{"tid":1502410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【正名】唔好叫黑警，以後叫「東廠走狗」","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:19:59.000Z","uid":270856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d68350b5fc08ccd1b434631fb1913129ff4a5d5","tid":1502410,"uid":270856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"見到巴絲提議叫犬隻 Geheime Staatspolizei（簡稱：Gestapo，蓋世太保），但「蓋世太保」4隻字嗌起上嚟好擇使。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGeheime Staatspolizei 意指秘密國家警察，「秘」「國」「察（賊）」聽落ok，但可能唔會一叫即明。<br />\n於是乎，我提議不如直接叫「東廠走狗」啦，簡單易明兼夠強國特色，popo聽到應該會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（wiki圖1、圖2、圖3）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/25/000329_db2ce3724795da4a15e0b8c5ed9df7ab.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F25%2F000329_db2ce3724795da4a15e0b8c5ed9df7ab.jpeg&h=7eb66534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFowqpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFowqpq.jpg&h=ef73572a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7K6Rqpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7K6Rqpq.jpg&h=93f53fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都是狗，不要分那樣細<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蓋世太保個名型啲啲"},{"pid":"bc72e8f1264aef0811f9960a838b06f87c622775","tid":1502410,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bad0e005b38271c3cf3cef6ef456b8f793adf4fc","tid":1502410,"uid":25573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"叫太監算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"aaead87eed85a1e1f509a486407f05d5a791594e","tid":1502410,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEhtr7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEhtr7b.png&h=d0ab0272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cef9efb1622438c7bcfab9917704b395b08b7d1","tid":1502410,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"畜生"},{"pid":"9f6a3cf83e3cefc478aa5ab1b6bb923fd732e428","tid":1502410,"uid":270856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:10:27.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%9C%E5%8E%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%259C%25E5%258E%2582&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84kYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=66efb226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%9C%E5%8E%82</a>"},{"pid":"cfe1a7f96138b6eb887f3ea3ca3aec4e5102edd6","tid":1502410,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"叫gestapopo 係俾外國傳媒扣佢地帽子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eccf617fd44768feb72a1f91dea33df0455230b","tid":1502410,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"我地今場運動證明左好多野，<br />\n證明左中聯辦治港<br />\n證明左警黑合作<br />\n證明左武警扮黑警<br />\n證明黑警會扮示威者<br />\n證明左狗鐵監控直駁狗總<br />\n再俾你地證明監控燈柱直駁大陸<br />\n仲證明左好多野！<br />\n然後呢？沒有然係，證明咁多野做咩？ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢場運動唔係捉錯處，唔係搵得越多就會贏。港共根本一步一步謀殺緊香港人。</span></span><br />\n場運動根本入左死局，示威者剩係識不停漫無目的咁上街示威，白白犧牲，然後港共就加強打壓。<br />\n咁樣係唔會贏架！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只有撃中港共弱點，先有資格同佢平起平坐講數。</strong></span></span><br />\n只有港共一跪，所有野先有機會平反，要撒監控唔係去發現佢監控，然後推低支燈柱，係要去解決個源頭，否則我地同大陸人有咩分別？<br />\n大陸人一樣知中共幾醜惡，但佢地推翻唔到，證明到個政府有幾邪惡係無用架！<br />\n明明已經有咁清晰嘅弱點暴露左出黎，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>機場就係港共春袋</strong></span></span><br />\n唔去打佢痛處，依然每星期動員去上街，叫叫口號拍拍手散水就可以？<br />\n然後再俾人捉幾十人去審？<br />\n經濟唔肯犧牲，時間唔肯犧牲，<br />\n旅客都唔可以犧牲。<br />\n咁只好犧牲我地年輕一代，犧牲佢地健康，<br />\n犧牲佢地健全，最後犧牲佢地性命先滿足？"}]}